Avr_meta is a C++ template library for embedded software development, primarily for AVR microcontroller.

    Content
avr_adc                           AVR ADC – Analog to Digital Converter
avr_debug                         AVR_DEBUG template
avr_interrupt/ext_int_control     AVR External Interrupts  control
avr_interrupt/pin_ch_int_control  AVR Pin Change Interrupt control
   
avr_misc                          miscellaneous functions
avr_pin                           AVR Pin control
avr_power_mgmt                    AVR Power Management
avr_spi                           AVR SPI – Serial Peripheral Interface
avr_twi                           AVR 2-wire Serial Interface (master operations only)
avr_usart                         AVR Universal Synchronous and Asynchronous serial Receiver and Transmitter (async operations only)

container/bit_field               C++ template bit field implementation
container/circular_buffer         Circular buffer implementation

event_driven                      Classes for use in event-driven software

meta                              Template metafunctions
misc                              Miscellaneous

state/led_blinker                 Led blinked mode (state) indicator
state/state_machine               State machine implementation for use in embedded software
state/switch_case                 Switch case statement template (used by state machine)



